{"tid":1042751,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屌 頭先搭巴士尾班車 去到總站車長冇叫醒我入左九巴車廠","createTime":"2019-03-01T18:19:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-01T23:59:33.000Z","uid":143346,"like":3,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ec96419290f4647eea11a9d9d846d5186224e8c6","tid":1042751,"uid":143346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T18:19:20.000Z","msg":"平時九龍灣搭尾班巴士返去藍田<br />\n之後攰得濟恰左陣 起身一睇 屌 點解又去左九龍灣既<br />\n成架車得我同司機 走去問佢 呢架唔係xxx路線咩<br />\n點解去左黎呢度 原來佢冇check清楚總站落曬客未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但我已經係坐係下層後排位置<br />\n之後佢都好似冇聲出 後尾話架車出返觀塘<br />\n但之後入完廠洗完車 又收左架車 話帶我搭其他車<br />\n車廠出個位咁岩又去返我平時返工附近既位<br />\n即係還原基本步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話帶我搭車其實係行好遠搭返通宵巴返去<br />\n之後算 搭的士返去 同個的士佬呻完<br />\n話我應該搞大件事 佢可以開架私家車車我返去<br />\n話曬佢冇好好check清楚係咪個個乘客落曬車"},{"pid":"be4fd07992816dcba13057f1cb50b447999dc709","tid":1042751,"uid":220701,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T18:21:25.000Z","msg":"有必要搞到咁大咩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c839bd82e6d14719cccd234f315490d3406aa251","tid":1042751,"uid":220701,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T18:22:35.000Z","msg":"「話我應該搞大件事 佢可以開架<span style=\"color: green;\">私家車</span>車我返去」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba4d82b524317b05c21d802906534ab341e65360","tid":1042751,"uid":118709,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T18:22:53.000Z","msg":"屌你自己訓著左唔記得起身都有責任啦<br />\n咪撚成個蝗蟲咁咩都要人老奉就你啦<br />\n一程的士當交學費囉屌"},{"pid":"ca33cf68f4a935b7debb988121d060b6195f9813","tid":1042751,"uid":191815,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T18:23:29.000Z","msg":"司機路一嘢扑濕你再搵個位踢你落車咪算好囉<br />\n仲想搞大件事？"},{"pid":"d2a089e8dad43b196f754cd7c8d7f1859e81801a","tid":1042751,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T18:23:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>司機唔一嘢扑濕你再搵個位踢你落車咪算好囉<br />\n仲想搞大件事？</blockquote>"},{"pid":"edda2b2ed61fe0f6932b1e46486805812bc57a1b","tid":1042751,"uid":199049,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T18:28:43.000Z","msg":"上次我都試過，在上層訓到唔知醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n成架巴士熄晒燈番廠途中，我行落去佢又聽唔到，之後我叫一聲司機佢成個人嚇到離一離<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後啦啦聲俾我落車，我都覺得唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"add40888079bd6e7931ed650ecda7130e1e5e944","tid":1042751,"uid":122623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c839bd82e6d14719cccd234f315490d3406aa251","tid":1042751,"uid":220701,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T18:22:35.000Z","msg":"「話我應該搞大件事 佢可以開架<span style=\"color: green;\">私家車</span>車我返去」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T18:40:46.000Z","msg":"應該指私牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />定公司車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ed327748f3c0e9d249d60d3316252469e908b4b","tid":1042751,"uid":22034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T21:22:39.000Z","msg":"我都試過<br />\n入到車廠洗緊車先醒，行去同個司機講佢嚇親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後車翻我去站頭，好彩住得近"},{"pid":"a12e2a043a264fa0c80ba3b7c9c2c29d8520b259","tid":1042751,"uid":115911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"add40888079bd6e7931ed650ecda7130e1e5e944","tid":1042751,"uid":122623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c839bd82e6d14719cccd234f315490d340